query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi_idx.info > '4.0' AND (k.keyword like '%evil%') AND n.gender in ('m') AND cct1.kind not in ('crew','complete+verified','cast') AND cct2.kind in ('complete','cast','crew') AND t.production_year > 1991 AND mi.info not in ('Vietnamese','English','Serbian','Slovenian','Portuguese','Chechen','Turkish','Urdu','Macedonian','Zulu','Welsh','Kalmyk-Oirat','Georgian') AND it2.info in ('LD video standard','LD spaciality','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','quotes','studios','production process protocol','sound mix','LD subtitles','bottom 10 rank','votes','soundtrack','rating','agent address','LD color rendition','nick names','trivia','gross','certificates','LD group genre','LD picture format','keywords') AND it1.info in ('LD video noise','opening weekend','LD audio quality')
